INSERT INTO DM.AF_FORE_QH (UTC_START_DATETIME, UTC_MODEL_QUERY_DATETIME, UTC_QUERY_DATETIME, MODEL_ID, DATA_TYPE_DICT_ID, DIM_DATA_TYPE_ID, LOCATION_ID, LEAD_TIME_QH, FORECASTED_VALUE)
SELECT
    T.UTC_START_DATETIME
    ,T.UTC_MODEL_QUERY_DATETIME
    ,T.UTC_QUERY_DATETIME
    ,T.MODEL_ID
    ,DIDT.DATA_TYPE_DICT_ID
    ,T.DIM_DATA_TYPE_ID
    ,T.LOCATION_ID
    ,T.LEAD_TIME_QH
    ,T.FORECASTED_VALUE
FROM
    DM.AF_FORE_QH_ISTVAN T
INNER JOIN
    DW.DW_DIM_DATA_TYPE DIDT
ON
    T.DIM_DATA_TYPE_ID = DIDT.ID

select 1
